snippet.title: STG Football Trailer
snippet.description:
Officially licensed by the NFLPA, STG Football is a free-to-play, real-time, arcade football game designed from the ground up! It is a true multiplayer game supporting unique 4v4 gameplay that emphasizes teamwork and strategy.

Join our discord and follow us on social media for the latest updates, including our upcoming Beta launch and Digital Player Pack sale. 

Discord: https://discord.gg/STGFootball 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/STG_Football 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/stgfootball_ 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/STG-Football... 
Website: https://stgfootball.com 
Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/superteam-football-6ce66c 
Whitepaper: https://superteam-games.gitbook.io/st... 
Medium: https://medium.com/@STG_Footbal
